The default Ansible configuration file is located under 
              /etc/ansible/ansible.cfg 

for getting this default files, while installing ansible your also install the following cmnd 
             $  sudo apt-add-repository ppa:ansible/ansible


 Most of Ansible's settings can be modified using this configuration file
  to meet the needs of your environment.


 $ vi /etc/ansible/ansible.cfg 

#  inside this file there will be a github repository link reg, config file plz browse it and
# copy the defaults section 

defaults:
#inventory_file = /etc/ansible/ansible.cfg 
if need to change the default inventory file we need to uncommend this line
and mention your inventory file name


